# Employee Management API (Service + Repository Pattern)

## 📌 Overview

This is a RESTful Web API built using ASP.NET Core that manages employee data.
The project follows the **Service Layer + Repository Pattern** to ensure clean architecture and separation of concerns.

---

## 🏗️ Architecture

Controller → Service Layer → Repository → DbContext → SQL Server

* **Controller**: Handles HTTP requests and responses
* **Service Layer**: Contains business logic
* **Repository**: Handles database operations
* **DbContext**: Connects to SQL Server using Entity Framework Core

---

## 📂 Project Structure

* Controllers/
* Services/
* Repositories/
* Models/
* Data/

---

## ⚙️ Features

* Get all employees
* Get employee by ID
* Create new employee
* Update employee
* Delete employee

